item.title: Salancia - Something New | Something Different
item.dc:creator: @janceboy janceboy
item.description:
@janceboy wrote:

Thank you for the feedback

  • Most bosses have the same feature that everyone gets the loot
  • The only items spawnable are in the tab so you dont have to waste time to buy them all from shop

[quote=“wimstr, post:13, topic:553597”]Feedback as of right now.

  • Client has a odd white border
  • Generic home
  • Exciting bosses (Mainly Bork because everyone gets a drop)
  • Disappointed you can set your levels and there are spawn tabs
  • Wildy level counter is very very strange (Random numbers)

I wouldn’t say the server is unique, but the server is set up different then most.
And it seems this server is mainly focused on teaming bosses, and obtaining customs.
Not sure if there’s any pvp or skilling side, but it can be enjoy-able for some people in the rsps community.[/quote]
